       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. VENDOR-RISK-ASSESSMENT.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-ZSERIES.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-ZSERIES.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-RISK-RATING                PIC X(8) VALUE "MODERATE".
       01  WS-RISK-REASON                PIC X(80) VALUE SPACES.
       01  WS-VENDOR-TOTAL-AWARDS        PIC 9(12) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-VENDOR-ACTIVE-CONTRACTS    PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-LARGEST-CONTRACT-VALUE     PIC 9(10) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-VENDOR-IS-SMALL-BIZ        PIC 9(1) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-YEARS-AS-VENDOR            PIC 9(3) VALUE ZERO.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
      *    RULE 1: NEW VENDOR WITH LARGE PORTFOLIO = HIGH RISK
           IF WS-YEARS-AS-VENDOR < 2
               AND WS-VENDOR-TOTAL-AWARDS >= 100000000
               MOVE "HIGH    " TO WS-RISK-RATING
               MOVE "NEW VENDOR WITH LARGE CUMULATIVE AWARDS"
                   TO WS-RISK-REASON
               GO TO ASSESSMENT-END
           END-IF

      *    RULE 2: CONCENTRATION RISK - TOO MANY ACTIVE CONTRACTS
           IF WS-VENDOR-ACTIVE-CONTRACTS >= 8
               MOVE "HIGH    " TO WS-RISK-RATING
               MOVE "EXCESSIVE ACTIVE CONTRACT CONCENTRATION"
                   TO WS-RISK-REASON
               GO TO ASSESSMENT-END
           END-IF

      *    RULE 3: SINGLE CONTRACT DOMINANCE
           IF WS-LARGEST-CONTRACT-VALUE >= 75000000
               MOVE "HIGH    " TO WS-RISK-RATING
               MOVE "SINGLE CONTRACT EXCEEDS DOMINANCE THRESHOLD"
                   TO WS-RISK-REASON
               GO TO ASSESSMENT-END
           END-IF

      *    RULE 4: SMALL BUSINESS WITH HIGH CUMULATIVE EXPOSURE
           IF WS-VENDOR-IS-SMALL-BIZ = 1
               AND WS-VENDOR-TOTAL-AWARDS >= 250000000
               MOVE "HIGH    " TO WS-RISK-RATING
               MOVE "SMALL BUSINESS EXCEEDS CUMULATIVE EXPOSURE LIMIT"
                   TO WS-RISK-REASON
               GO TO ASSESSMENT-END
           END-IF

      *    RULE 5: MODERATE FLAGS
           IF WS-VENDOR-ACTIVE-CONTRACTS >= 4
               MOVE "MODERATE" TO WS-RISK-RATING
               MOVE "ELEVATED ACTIVE CONTRACT COUNT"
                   TO WS-RISK-REASON
               GO TO ASSESSMENT-END
           END-IF

           IF WS-VENDOR-TOTAL-AWARDS >= 300000000
               MOVE "MODERATE" TO WS-RISK-RATING
               MOVE "CUMULATIVE AWARDS APPROACHING WATCH LEVEL"
                   TO WS-RISK-REASON
               GO TO ASSESSMENT-END
           END-IF

      *    RULE 6: LOW RISK - ALL CHECKS PASSED
           MOVE "LOW     " TO WS-RISK-RATING
           MOVE "ALL RISK INDICATORS WITHIN ACCEPTABLE RANGE"
               TO WS-RISK-REASON.

       ASSESSMENT-END.
           GOBACK.
